### The Two Portals

**Cactus Portal** — client-facing
Shipments, tracking, meter balance, invoices, AI insights.
Never shows markup, raw costs, or carrier account details.

**The Alamo** — internal Cactus admin only
- Org + carrier account management
- Invoice upload, AI normalization, human review
- Dispute review and resolution
- Rate card management
- Audit logs, meter health

Invoice display rules per carrier_account_mode (v1.6.0):
  lassoed → ONLY final_billed_rate shown to client
  dark → carrier_charge + final_billed_rate shown
  Checked per line item, not per invoice or per org

