## 14. DESIGN SYSTEM — THE ALAMO & CACTUS PORTAL

### Design Philosophy
Crisp lines. Clean spacing. Less noise. Detail-oriented.
Stripe-level data density for The Alamo.
Apple-level restraint for the Cactus Portal.
Same system, different spacing expression.
No pure black. No shadows. No gradients. Always 0.5px borders.

### The Three Brand Colors
Forest  #2D5A27 — operational, active, confirmed, primary CTA
Amber   #D97706 — client-facing warmth, savings highlights, Portal CTA
Bloom   #D81B7A — warnings, disputes, held items, attention required

The cactus in full expression:
  Forest = the plant. Grounded, alive, resilient.
  Amber  = the desert sun. Warm, energetic, inviting.
  Bloom  = the flower. Striking, urgent, beautiful.

